 우물 천장고를 적용해 세대 내부의 개방감을 극대화했다.\n\n현대건설 관계자는 “‘OWN THE NEW’ 비전 아래 압구정5구역이 지닌 한강변 입지의 가치를 혁신적인 방식으로 구현하고자 했다”며 “전 세대 100% 한강 조망을 실현하는 데 그치지 않고, 조망의 폭과 깊이까지 끌어올려 새로운 압구정 현대의 프리미엄을 완성하겠다”고 밝혔다.","url":"http://www.wowtv.co.kr/NewsCenter/News/Read?articleId=A202605080526&t=NN","published_at":"2026-05-08T14:15:00","sentiment":"positive","is_new":true}],"disclosures":[{"date":"2026-05-08T16:57:29","title":"[기재정정]단일판매ㆍ공급계약체결              ","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260508800984","is_new":true},{"date":"2026-05-07T11:19:12","title":"임원ㆍ주요주주특정증권등소유상황보고서","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260507000203","is_new":false}],"reports":[],"consensus":{"Q":{"period":"2026년 2분기","latest":197510526315.79,"is_new":false,"series":[{"date":"2026-04-08","value":189964705882.35},{"date":"2026-04-09","value":190064705882.35},{"date":"2026-04-13","value":191182352941.18},{"date":"2026-04-14","value":190982352941.18},{"date":"2026-04-15","value":191394117647.06},{"date":"2026-04-16","value":191158823529.41},{"date":"2026-04-20","value":192394117647.06},{"date":"2026-04-21","value":191816666666.66998},{"date":"2026-04-24","value":191405263157.88998},{"date":"2026-04-29","value":199635000000.0},{"date":"2026-04-30","value":198585000000.0},{"date":"2026-05-06","value":197510526315.79}]},"Y":{"period":"2026년","latest":826805000000.0,"is_new":false,"series":[{"date":"2026-04-08","value":818276190476.19},{"date":"2026-04-09","value":814176190476.19},{"date":"2026-04-13","value":810795238095.24},{"date":"2026-04-14","value":809680952380.95},{"date":"2026-04-15","value":810828571428.5701},{"date":"2026-04-16","value":809590476190.48},{"date":"2026-04-20","value":807066666666.6699},{"date":"2026-04-21","value":810735000000.0},{"date":"2026-04-24","value":812285714285.71},{"date":"2026-04-29","value":826757142857.1399},{"date":"2026-04-30","value":826423809523.81},{"date":"2026-05-06","value":826805000000.0}]}},"stk_flow":[{"date":"2026-05-08","외인":16484089